[semihtml][title]Your Activism Cause Here[/title]
The Lovinity Community+ aims to be a community that promotes activist causes and movements. Everyone who uses our website is free to promote positive activist movements. However, if you would like <strong>an activist section on our website</strong>, you may contact us via. support tickets (About -&gt; Support Tickets, or email support@lovinity.org ). By getting an activist section / page on our website, your cause will gain extra exposure as well as the use of our website features. Here are some of the possible <strong>features</strong> we can delegate to your activist section / page:

<ul>
	<li>Club user group (so people can show their support via. their profile) (All activism sections will get a club/usergroup by default)</li>
	<li>Forums (all activism sections will get a forum by default)</li>
	<li>Advertising banners (for a fee)</li>
	<li>Events Calendar</li>
	<li>Catalogues / forms / databases</li>
	<li>Chat rooms</li>
	<li>Downloads</li>
	<li>Audio / Video / Image galleries</li>
	<li>Links library</li>
	<li>News</li>
	<li>Web Pages (Comcode pages)</li>
	<li>Polls</li>
	<li>Wikis</li>
	<li>Internet Radio Show</li>
</ul>

